&lt;li&gt;Hands-on expertise in observability practices and tools (e.g., Prometheus, Grafana, ELK stack) and familiarity with SRE principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with CI/CD pipelines and automation tools (e.g., Jenkins, GitLab CI) and Infrastructure as Code practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of cloud platforms (AWS and/or GCP) and container orchestration (Kubernetes), and experience building scalable systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong collaboration and communication skills, with experience working across teams (development, QA, product).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for automation, reliability, and developer efficiency, with a mindset of continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
